# Changelog & documentation gate

When completing a development phase or shipping a user-visible / structural change set:

1. Update `CHANGELOG.md` in the same change set (`Added` / `Changed` / `Fixed` / `Security` as appropriate)
2. Update `ROADMAP.md` status when a phase starts or finishes
3. Update `KNOWN_ISSUES.md` when introducing or resolving tracked debt
4. Update `DECISIONS.md` only for approved architectural decisions
5. Bump root `package.json` version when cutting a release per `VERSIONING.md`

Do not mark phase work complete without the changelog entry.
